---
import CourseLayout from '../layouts/CourseLayout.astro';
---

<CourseLayout title="Module 4: Policies & Procedures" currentModule={4}>
  
  <span class="text-sky-600 font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm">Topic 4 of 6</span>
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mt-2 mb-8">Department Policies & Procedures</h1>

  <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none">
    
    <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">
      Compliance isn't just paperwork; it's the law. Following these Office of Long-Term Living (OLTL) requirements ensures we can continue providing care to our community.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow border-t-4 border-t-sky-500">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">1. The Care Plan (PCSP)</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
          <strong>Rule:</strong> Services must match the Participant Care Service Plan exactly.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-2">
          If the plan says "Meal Prep" and "Bathing," you cannot spend 4 hours cleaning the garage. Unauthorized tasks are not billable and put the agency at risk.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow border-t-4 border-t-sky-500">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">2. EVV (Electronic Visit Verification)</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
          <strong>Rule:</strong> You must clock in and out using the agency app at the participant's location.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-2">
          The 21st Century Cures Act requires GPS verification. If you clock in from your own home, it is flagged as fraud.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow border-t-4 border-t-sky-500">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">3. Reporting Status Changes</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
          <strong>Rule:</strong> If their health changes, tell us.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-2">
          If a participant is hospitalized, you must notify the office immediately. We cannot bill for services while a participant is in the hospital.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow border-t-4 border-t-sky-500">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">4. Universal Precautions</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
          <strong>Rule:</strong> Treat all bodily fluids as infectious.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-2">
          Wear gloves when assisting with toileting or bathing. Wash your hands immediately upon arrival and before leaving.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="flex justify-between items-center pt-8 border-t border-slate-200">
        <a href="/module-3" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-sky-600 font-semibold flex items-center gap-2">
            ← Previous: Complaint Resolution
        </a>
        <a href="/module-5" class="bg-sky-600 hover:bg-sky-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg flex items-center gap-2">
            Next: Quality Management →
        </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</CourseLayout>